			Company Description 


			The Singing Machine Co., Inc. engages in the development, production, marketing and distribution of consumer karaoke audio equipment, accessories, musical instruments and licensed youth electronic products. Its brands include The Singing Machine, SMDigital, SoundX and Home. The company sells its pro...
		


                The Singing Machine Co., Inc. engages in the development, production, marketing and distribution of consumer karaoke audio equipment, accessories, musical instruments and licensed youth electronic products. Its brands include The Singing Machine, SMDigital, SoundX and Home. The company sells its products in North America, Europe, Australia and Central South America. The Singing Machine was founded in 1982 and is headquartered in Fort Lauderdale, FL.
            




