#SingingMachineHome



Home™
Bluetooth® Speaker






Elegantly designed, acoustically engineered for rich, soulful Bluetooth® audio delivery When you're ready to make the transformation to in-home karaoke, The Singing Machine Home™ is ready for you, on-demand.



#SingingMachineClassic



Home™
Wi-Fi karaoke






Get your party started on demand with built-in Wi-Fi for instant high definition karaoke music video streaming hosted in the cloud and available through Singing Machine Play Queue.



#SoundX

Home™ Play Queue


You'll be sure not to miss a beat by creating the perfect playlist with Play Queue. Set up your list from your Singing Machine Home™ or by signing into your account from a computer.






Music SM Classic




KARAOKE COMMUNITY
							




Take part in the Karaoke Revolution by choosing from one of four membership options. Then watch, rate, share, and create videos from our huge song library. Listeners from around the world are waiting to become your fans. Join us now!






Register Products

 REGISTER PRODUCTS



We want you to enjoy your Singing Machine purchase to the fullest. Please take a couple minutes to register by filling out a simple form. You will then receive efficient support, important updates, and more related to your products. 




Singing Machine Cafe

 SINGING MACHINE CAFE


 
Here we serve you with the freshest company announcements and updates. Our news section, blog posts, and social media feeds will have you up-to-date with everything you need to know from the world of Singing Machine.













