Discover the Karaoke Download Store
Singing Machine, premium partner of Stingray Karaoke, is pleased to offer you a new and improved Karaoke Store. More than 11,000 karaoke videos in the style of today’s top-charting artists and yesterday’s legends, in Pop, Rock, Country, R&B/Hip-Hop and more are available to download.
For help on finding music for your system, please select your Singing Machine from the list below to find the music download instructions for your system.








Select your product to register and get your FREE promo code to start downloading your favorite music

















































































FOLLOW THESE EASY STEPS (CD+G Format)

Register your machine at singingmachine.com to receive your FREE downloads promo code
Visit the Karaoke Store
Signup for an account and when prompted, enter the Promo Code you received via email. Song Credits will be added to your account
Select "SMC" as your preferred file format
Search, Add to Cart, and Purchase Songs using your Song Credits
Click "My Library" and download your karaoke videos to your computer
Install and launch SMC Karaoke Manager software for Microsoft Windows (click on Create your own CD+G) (Additional software is required for Macintosh computers to burn CDGs).
In the SMC Karaoke Manager, add the SMC files to your Song Library
Follow the SMC Karaoke Manager instructions to burn your favorite songs to CD.



FOLLOW THESE EASY STEPS (MP3+G Format)

Download and install the Karaoke Store Application
Create an account and register your machine. Song Credits will be added automatically to your account to access your Free Songs.
Select MP3+G as your preferred File Format
Plug your own USB Drive to your computer
Search, Add to Cart and Purchase Songs using Song Credits
Downloading to USB Drive will start automatically or you can manually download each song from "MY LIBRARY"
Unplug the USB drive from your computer and plug it into your Singing Machine Karaoke Machine and start singing



FOLLOW THESE EASY STEPS (Bluetooth)
*Requires an iOS device (e.g. iPad or iPhone)

From your mobile device, download the “Singing Machine Mobile Karaoke App” from the App Store
Using Bluetooth, pair your mobile device to your karaoke machine
Access the Singing Machine Karaoke App and start singing!


 






Select your product and start downloading your favorite music





















FOLLOW THESE EASY STEPS

Plug the SMC USB Flash Drive into your computer
Install and launch the Karaoke Store Application
Create an account and follow the onscreen instructions. Enter the promo code printed on your Welcome Kit (located inside the box) to redeem your FREE karaoke songs. Song Credits will be added to your account.
Select MP4 as your preferred file format.
Search, Add to cart, and Purchase using Song Credits.
Click on "My Library" and add your purchases to your Mic Guy USB stick into your laptop or computer.
Unplug your USB memory stick from your computer and plug into your Singing Machine Karaoke Machine and start singing!


Microsoft Windows 10 does not currently support the Singing Machine Karaoke Manager.  Contact our customer service for other options that may be available.
 






Select your product and start downloading your favorite music






FOLLOW THESE EASY STEPS

Register your Singing Machine Play account and click on the " Register"" button in the top right hand corner.
Connect your SMC Home unit to your TV (via HDMI cable), connect to your WiFi router, and login to Singing Machine Play with the account info you created above.
Upon your first login, your first FREE month will be automatically credited to your account.


 




